{"tid":1806114,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Steam 2019 最受歡迎遊戲《隻狼》《GTAV》等上白金榜","createTime":"2020-01-01T05:34:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T02:20:41.000Z","uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8b71c732b27dd760e40eea5d8fd3f60d45bfae0b","tid":1806114,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T05:34:13.000Z","msg":"2019 年還有兩天就正式結束，不少公司亦趕於在年底前公佈自己的數據。在今個月 27 日，Steam 亦公佈了今年自己的百大暢銷遊戲名單，雖然遊戲被分為四類以及未有透露實際的數字以及排名，但從登上白金排行榜的十二款遊戲而言，動作、射擊以及電競三大類型仍然成為玩家們的最愛。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/1-14.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2F1-14.png&h=f722b220&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSteam 在是次的公佈中將一眾遊戲分成四個類別，分別為白金、黃金、白銀以及青銅，當中最暢銷的遊戲則會被納入白金類別。一如去年的趨勢，不少曾舉辦電競比賽的遊戲如《絕對武力：全球攻勢》（CS:GO）、《Dota 2》、《Battlegrounds》以及《Tom Clancy&rsquo;s Rainbow Six Siege》亦成為了白金類別當中的遊戲，反映出人氣度有增無減。該類別內亦加入了不少於今年間冒起的遊戲，例如《隻狼》以及《Monster Hunter: World》等，證明受到廣泛玩家的歡迎。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/1-14.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2F1-14.png&h=f722b220&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n至於在次一級的黃金類別當中，《生化危機 2 重製版》以及《刺客教條：奧德賽》等曾推出電影的遊戲亦成功上榜，至於在近期推出電視劇集的《The Witcher 3: Wild Hunt》亦被列入為黃金的類別，未知是否受電視劇集引起的熱潮所影響。值得一提的是，在 11 月才推出的《Star Wars 絕地：組織殞落》亦成功躋身入這個類別，可見遊戲的受歡迎程度。"},{"pid":"fa6337380a5604d93f7d37f4ff7a6351dee90cc2","tid":1806114,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T05:35:31.000Z","msg":"Star Wars 絕地：組織殞落<br />\n垃圾EA<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b024155da964c426bec5be3ec1368c7ee148dd1","tid":1806114,"uid":85180,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"fa6337380a5604d93f7d37f4ff7a6351dee90cc2","tid":1806114,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T05:35:31.000Z","msg":"Star Wars 絕地：組織殞落<br />\n垃圾EA<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T05:46:29.000Z","msg":"玩爆機都係個幾張公廁圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5026100dc374f5726788932bc45d9d008ec90ba9","tid":1806114,"uid":15939,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T10:39:24.000Z","msg":"慘喇㥇喇，Witcher 得黃金，肯定比連登仔屌到化"},{"pid":"563947863958e769a2c190845852d347b0b604c4","tid":1806114,"uid":185712,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T19:00:28.000Z","msg":"Total war三國<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e1150f1df1d62b7b0ae6899d4e82ae278a56162","tid":1806114,"uid":82889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1b024155da964c426bec5be3ec1368c7ee148dd1","tid":1806114,"uid":85180,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"fa6337380a5604d93f7d37f4ff7a6351dee90cc2","tid":1806114,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T05:35:31.000Z","msg":"Star Wars 絕地：組織殞落<br />\n垃圾EA<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T05:46:29.000Z","msg":"玩爆機都係個幾張公廁圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T00:15:35.000Z","msg":"唔好沖出黎柒啦"},{"pid":"9a66683c099ee1a58c2075c0ff224d5fdf3bd481","tid":1806114,"uid":82889,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"5026100dc374f5726788932bc45d9d008ec90ba9","tid":1806114,"uid":15939,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T10:39:24.000Z","msg":"慘喇㥇喇，Witcher 得黃金，肯定比連登仔屌到化"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T00:16:41.000Z","msg":"出左五年冇online mode仲黃金緊都屌？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nChing邊到平行時空<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e071cdd909e001c8764af7e8308eb24b2ca676f","tid":1806114,"uid":21646,"like":0,"dislike":